      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-ric-sel-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice cliente                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
